722666f-a.title: Manhattan: Prince Street - Mott Street
722666f-a.text:
(1)
Prince Street, north side, west from and including Mott, to and
including Mulberry Streets. The view shows the Roman Catholic Churh
of St. Patrick.
Augst 1, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The ssme, showing Prince Street, north side, east from and
including Mulberry, to and including Mott Streets. Also shown
is Mott Street, at, adjoining and north of the N.E. corner of
Prince Street.
August 28, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
